{"tid":2212673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國將實行防沉迷法 晚上10時至早上8時禁止網絡遊戲","createTime":"2020-09-22T04:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T05:32:54.000Z","uid":36494,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7d32b14489800e766a943d321478479974e1d6b0","tid":2212673,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"為防止民眾沈迷網絡遊戲，9月12日開始中國內地實施防止未成年人沉迷網絡遊戲法例，首先多方面禁止未成年玩家沉迷網絡遊戲，同時要求實行網絡遊戲帳號實名註冊制度。除此之外法例規定每日夜晚10時至到早上8時不得為未成年人提供遊戲服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2757738/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E5%AF%A6%E8%A1%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E6%B3%95%20%20%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A10%E6%99%82%E8%87%B3%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A8%E6%99%82%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2?fbclid=IwAR0kgL7ADx7lR-HqyNte2Yj0cHW59uIzG6rAFzdODxcwkhJjGVyhiJvepzU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2757738%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%25B2%2589%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%2520%2520%25E6%2599%259A%25E4%25B8%258A10%25E6%2599%2582%25E8%2587%25B3%25E6%2597%25A9%25E4%25B8%258A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E9%2581%258A%25E6%2588%25B2%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0kgL7ADx7lR-HqyNte2Yj0cHW59uIzG6rAFzdODxcwkhJjGVyhiJvepzU&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zESPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=3193870c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2757738/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E5%AF%A6%E8%A1%8C%E9%98%B2%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E6%B3%95%20%20%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A10%E6%99%82%E8%87%B3%E6%97%A9%E4%B8%8A8%E6%99%82%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2?fbclid=IwAR0kgL7ADx7lR-HqyNte2Yj0cHW59uIzG6rAFzdODxcwkhJjGVyhiJvepzU</a>"},{"pid":"11bf90cee9fb9722643536921ad5955bd570b59f","tid":2212673,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"咁玩單機game囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd092df6e0c0ac021fcb21ec95227108a152c58","tid":2212673,"uid":4285,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要早過灰姑娘瞓教"},{"pid":"227870d42100979f1d3fae9bcbd0f907cfd5870b","tid":2212673,"uid":39365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:03:51.000Z","msg":"咁咪朝早8點打到晚上10點囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正大陸大把人失業或者係三和大神"},{"pid":"82679525e849cc5e8dac6764f4f3e7b4326808b5","tid":2212673,"uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:04:08.000Z","msg":"對使用時間有規管，新法例對遊戲題材、內容、及玩法都加上限制，主要不允許色情、血腥、及暴力等遊戲。 消息一出，內地Xbox用家開始擔心要完成認證過程才能夠進行遊戲，不過境外版的實體光碟則不能正常進行遊戲<br />\n<br />\n亦有玩家擔心遊戲商可能因為防沉迷等法規不再推出中國版遊戲，更擔心購買中國版Xbox浪費金錢，因為很多遊戲都可能不再支援中國版Xbox。"},{"pid":"329d349baa5c2b61a3bc72cc224946e04f34fdde","tid":2212673,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"好搞笑"},{"pid":"676db90b8c8846e5ac240b60da8a14669947838a","tid":2212673,"uid":273791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"小粉紅又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1222716043cb7b577a898621581ebb1e872d4c","tid":2212673,"uid":307010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"借老豆個帳玩囉 老豆玩老母咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f33eec8aa41b14b8d194ad882f54e480f7b6fc1","tid":2212673,"uid":30084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"以後香港正常網路時間 10到8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f93794f0b6b547c2feb8a38f0d3cf9815f11dce","tid":2212673,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0